    <string name="settings_realtime_intro">When granted, Mangako notices new .cbz files within a second of them landing in your watched folders — same approach as Nextcloud\'s auto-upload. Without it the watcher relies on the system\'s 15-minute periodic schedule plus a refresh whenever you open the app.</string>
