    <string name="settings_section_battery">Background reliability</string>
    <string name="settings_battery_intro">Android Doze and aggressive OEM battery savers (Samsung, Xiaomi, OnePlus, etc.) can defer scans and notifications for hours when the screen is off. Whitelisting Mangako lets the 15-minute scan and upload retries fire on time. On Samsung / Xiaomi / Huawei, also visit the system battery settings for this app and disable any "deep sleep" or "auto-optimise" toggle.</string>
